\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The Four Pillars:
\f1\b0  1. 
\f4\b Automation:
\f1\b0  Eliminating manual tasks (even saving 1 minute counts!). 2. 
\f4\b Continuous Testing:
\f1\b0  Checking code at every step, not just at the end. 3. 
\f4\b Quality Control:
\f1\b0  Using "Quality Gates" to ensure only good code moves forward. 4. 
\f4\b Continuous Monitoring:
\f1\b0  Watching the app in real-time after it's live.\
