\fs42\fsmilli21333 \cf0 Analogy for Memorization: The "Office Building" Analogy
\f1\b0 \

\fs29\fsmilli14667 Let's use a secure office building to understand the concepts of public and private IPs and the SSH connection process.\

\f4\b The Goal:
\f1\b0  You need to get to your office (the virtual machine) inside a large, secure building (the AWS data center).\

\f4\b 1. The "Public vs. Private IP Address" Concept
\f1\b0 \
