\f1\b0 , the owner of the diary, can open it and write in it.\
\ls53\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	
\f8 \uc0\u9702 
\f1 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
0: Your 
\f4\b friends or family
\f1\b0  (other people in your group) cannot open or read the diary.\
\ls53\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	
\f8 \uc0\u9702 
\f1 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
0: 
\f4\b Strangers
