The lambda_handler function
\f1\b0  is the specific task you're doing right now, which is to take inventory.
\f4\b \
\ls95\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
filters
