\ls120\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	6	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Shell Executables (bash, ksh, sh, dash): Linux offers various shell executables to run scripts, such as bash, ksh, sh, and dash. While they perform similar functions, they have syntax differences.\
\ls120\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	7	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
