Case Study: Automating Node Health Monitoring\uc0\u8232 
\f1\b0 A DevOps engineer named John, working for Amazon, is responsible for 10,000 Linux virtual machines (VMs). He frequently receives complaints from developers about performance issues like high CPU or memory usage.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls148\ilvl1\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
