\f2\b\fs36 \cf3 \strokec3 1. Project Management & The SDLC\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf3 The 
\f2\b Software Development Life Cycle (SDLC)
\f0\b0  is the structured process for designing, developing, and testing high-quality software.\
