\f2\b Phases
\f0\b0 : Planning (defining scope/resources), Defining (documenting requirements in an SRS), Designing (HLD/LLD architecture), Building (coding), Testing (bug fixing), and Deployment. \uc0\u8232 \
\ls280\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 \uc0\u8232 
\f2\b Goal
\f0\b0 : Deliver products that meet customer expectations within time and cost estimates. \uc0\u8232 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

