\ls290\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	46	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Environment Variables and Application Configuration: Environment variables are used to store sensitive information and configuration settings for applications. These files are not included in repositories for security reasons and must be set up manually on the server.\
