\f5 \uc0\u9702 
\f4 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Distributed VCS (DVCS):
\f1\b0  Every developer has a complete copy of the entire repository on their local machine. This allows them to work offline, and they can collaborate directly with peers without needing a central server.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
