A 
\f4\b CVCS
\f1\b0  is like a 
\f4\b single shared office whiteboard
\f1\b0 . Everyone must work on the same board, and you can't work on the project if you're not at the office.\
\ls290\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	
\f8 \uc0\u9702 
\f1 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
A 
\f4\b DVCS
\f1\b0  is like 
\f4\b everyone having their own personal whiteboard
\f1\b0 . You can work on your copy at home or on a plane. When you are ready, you bring your whiteboard to the main meeting room to sync with the others.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls290\ilvl1
\f4\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Example:
