\f4\b bouncer at a nightclub
\f1\b0 . The nightclub is your server, and the bouncer is the security group. The bouncer has a list of rules (ports) about who is allowed to enter. If a person (traffic) tries to get in through a door that isn't on the list, they are denied entry.\
\ls290\ilvl1
\f4\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
