Why this Project Matters
\f1\b0 \
\ls292\ilvl0
\fs29\fsmilli14667 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Abhishek explains the purpose of the session: to show how a student with limited professional experience can create a project and showcase it on their resume. The goal is to demystify the process of building and deploying a real-world application, proving that it\'92s achievable with a little research and hands-on effort. Kunal's project, a Node.js application, serves as the perfect example.\
\ls292\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\'a0\
